{"tid":1917690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由西班牙回大陸之學生證實確診  昨乘國泰抵港  經深圳灣到東莞","createTime":"2020-03-09T15:24:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T15:42:06.000Z","uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4b17b5c01a2cc2f709a830e2a1fb03110601bc85","tid":1917690,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情持續，東莞市衛生健康局今日（9日）公布，新增一宗境外輸入確診病例。患者為中國留學生，上周六（7日）從西班牙乘坐國泰航班CX320回國，周日（8日）到達香港國際機場，在深圳灣口岸入境內地，體溫正常，口岸對其進行檢測，今日結果呈陽性。<br />\n<br />\n當局表示，患者目前已轉入東莞市第九人民醫院隔離治療，已初步找到6名密切接觸者，均已集中隔離觀察。省衛生健康委員會已將相關情況通報香港衛生部門。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200309/s00001/1583766425837/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E8%A5%BF%E7%8F%AD%E7%89%99%E8%BF%94%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E6%98%A8%E4%B9%98%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E6%8A%B5%E6%B8%AF%E7%B6%93%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E7%81%A3%E5%88%B0%E6%9D%B1%E8%8E%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200309%2Fs00001%2F1583766425837%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%258F%25AD%25E7%2589%2599%25E8%25BF%2594%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E6%2598%25A8%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%258F%25AD%25E6%258A%25B5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%259C%25B3%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%258E%259E&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=3fdaaaa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200309%2Fs00001%2F1583766425837%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%258F%25AD%25E7%2589%2599%25E8%25BF%2594%25E5%2585%